{"tid":484394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"培正發聲明讚揚呂麗瑤勇敢　3周前知悉即時停止外聘教練","createTime":"2017-11-30T04:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T06:40:04.000Z","uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4f52e2eeb2948cbcb3b274aa821d616b9c1d853a","tid":484394,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T04:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2017/11/1512011074_DP-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2017%2F11%2F1512011074_DP-1280w.jpg&h=c693043c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2017/11/1512011072_7q-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2017%2F11%2F1512011072_7q-1280w.jpg&h=26ed9a4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港女子跨欄運動員呂麗瑤在個人社交網頁，報稱十多年前被當時的教練性侵犯。她當年就讀的培正中學早上發表聲明，對其不幸遭遇深感難過，並對性侵兒童的施害者予以嚴厲讉責。<br />\n<br />\n培正表示，呂麗瑤約3星期前主動向校方透露將會公開事件，學校知悉後已即時停止有關外聘教練的工作，以及提供輔導和密切留意學生情緒。培正指，對於呂麗瑤勇敢地剖白，以其喚起大眾對兒童性侵的關注及鼓勵受害者勇敢站出來，校方全力支持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/培正發聲明讚揚呂麗瑤勇敢-3周前知悉即時停止外聘教練-105937\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E5%9F%B9%E6%AD%A3%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%E8%AE%9A%E6%8F%9A%E5%91%82%E9%BA%97%E7%91%A4%E5%8B%87%E6%95%A2-3%E5%91%A8%E5%89%8D%E7%9F%A5%E6%82%89%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E5%A4%96%E8%81%98%E6%95%99%E7%B7%B4-105937&d=AbwvgHSBefXHsD12AOHk78n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=9d4e6fca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/培正發聲明讚揚呂麗瑤勇敢-3周前知悉即時停止外聘教練-105937</a><br />\n<br />\n培正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2332640b0c71d29c0e52a80efe37e8a69f89fdc0","tid":484394,"uid":130105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T04:52:57.000Z","msg":"唔報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ac7a210a5250e8540aaf5674b070d55f196ef9","tid":484394,"uid":2707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T06:40:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有啲政治人物都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}